> looks like some recent change in container-libs is affecting libpod/container_config.go . https://github.com/containers/podman/pull/27271/checks?check_run_id=54725210511 .

That’s unrelated to everything else. This was commented as deprecated back in 002673d22f4afd2ee2c1c15aeac3b3b9ae65e225 , but the deprecation was not visible to tools — and now it is.

@Luap99 what needs to be done here? Git log suggests that we have removed even the backwards compatibility functionality, and the field is not hooked up to anything any more.
